tment%20banking%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotak.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FKotak%2Fabout-us%2Fexecutive-board%2FKotak_Shanti_Ekambaram%2520_Profile.pdf%5C%22%3EShanti%20Ekambaram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20head%20of%20consumer%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrakash%20Apte%2C%20chairman%20of%20KMB%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotak.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FKotak%2Fabout-us%2Fmedia-press-releases%2F2023%2FCEO-Appointment-Final.pdf%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20pleased%20to%20announce%20that%20%5Bthe%5D%20RBI%20has%20approved%20the%20appointment%20of%20Ashok%20Vaswani%20as%20the%20next%20MD%20and%20CEO%20of%20KMB.%20Ashok%20is%20a%20global%20banking%20leader%20with%20a%20proven%20track%20record%20of%20building%20and%20growing%20businesses%20at%20an%20international%20scale%20and%20has%20successfully%20steered%20organisations%20to%20greater%20heights.%20We%20are%20confident%20that%20Ashok%20will%20accelerate%20change%20and%20drive%20growth%20at%20Kotak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUday%20Kotak%2C%20founder%20and%20director%2C%20KMB%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fudaykotak%2Fstatus%2F1715663361277296851%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20am%20delighted%20that%20the%20RBI%20has%20approved%20our%20recommendation%2C%20Ashok%20Vaswani%2C%20as%20the%20next%20CEO%20of%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank.%20Ashok%20is%20a%20world%20class%20leader%20and%20banker%20with%20digital%20and%20customer%20focus.%20I%20am%20proud%20that%20we%20bring%20a%20%E2%80%98Global%20Indian%E2%80%99%20home%20to%20build%20Kotak%20and%20India%20of%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fhigh-attrition-rate-at-kotak-mahindra-bank-fails-to-find-a-spot-in-annual-report%5C%22%3EThe%20Issue%20of%20High%20Attrition%20Rate%20at%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20Fails%20to%20Find%20a%20Spot%20in%20Annual%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIgnoring%20int