to%20succeed%20Uday%20Kotak.%20Even%20if%20the%20Nomination%20and%20Remuneration%20Committee%20had%20admitted%20its%20failure%20in%20grooming%20younger%20internal%20talent%20for%20CEO%20succession%2C%20they%20could%20have%20shortlisted%20external%20executives%20in%20their%20mid-50s%20who%20have%20an%20exposure%20to%20Indian%20banking%2C%20and%20brought%20them%20in%20as%20executive%20directors%20at%20an%20earlier%20date%2C%20in%20order%20to%20expose%20them%20to%20KMB%E2%80%99s%20work%20environment%2C%20culture%20and%20senior%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20Vaswani%2C%20with%20negligible%20experience%20in%20Indian%20banking%2C%20will%20be%20parachuted%20from%20a%20pleasant%20retirement%20from%20global%20commercial%20banking%20directly%20into%20the%20KMB%20CEO%20post.%20On%20landing%2C%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20do%20wonders%20in%20implementing%20a%20digital%20strategy%20in%20the%20Indian%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20alternative%20explanation%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20Vaswani%20is%20that%20he%20was%20a%20last-minute%20selection%3B%20the%20banking%20regulator%2C%20the%20RBI%2C%20may%20have%20informed%20the%20KMB%20board%20that%20it%20would%20not%20approve%20an%20internal%20candidate%2C%20as%20it%20was%20uncomfortable%20with%20Uday%20Kotak%E2%80%99s%20continuance%20on%20the%20board%20as%20a%20non-executive%20director.%20This%20analyst%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhemindrahazari.com%2F2023%2F04%2F19%2Fafter-twenty-years-kotak-mahindra-bank-still-cant-manage-without-uday-kotak%2F%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Uday%20Kotak%E2%80%99s%20retention%20on%20the%20board%20as%20a%20non-executive%20non-independent%20director%20would%20make%20him%20effectively%20the%20back-seat%20driver%20of%20the%20bank%2C%20without%20any%20of%20the%20associated%20responsibilities%20that%20come%20with%20such%20a%20position.%20It%20is%20poor%20corporate%20governance%20to%20allow%20a%20long-serving%20promoter%20CEO%20to%20continue%20on%20the%20board%20as%20a%20non-executive%20director%20after%20stepping%20down%20as%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Vaswani%E2%80%99s%20selection%20was%20made%20under%20such%20circumstances%2C%20on%20account%20of%20Uday%20Kotak%E2%80%99s%20continuance%20on%20the%20board%2C%20then%20again%20the%20Nomination%20and%20Remuneration%20Committee%20and%20the%20board%20have%20to%20be%20held%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20KMB%E2%80%99s%20stock%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fearnings%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank-q2-fy24-why-the-underperformance-should-reverse-11585271.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20underperforming%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20compared%20to%20Nifty-50%20and%20Bank%20Nifty.%20This%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20apprehensions%20regarding%20a%20leadership%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20market%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20an%20insider%20to%20succeed%20Uday%20Kotak%2C%20as%20it%20would%20have%20indicated%20continuity%20in%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20strategy.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20market%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20senior%20executives.%20The%20announcement%20of%20a%20relatively%20unknown%20external%20candidate%2C%20with%20negligible%20experience%20in%20Indian%20banking%2C%20and%20who%20had%20apparently%20retired%20from%20commercial%20banking%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20the%20stock%20market%20even%20more%20apprehensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKMB%E2%80%99s%20share%20price%20versus%20Nifty-50%20and%20Bank%20Nifty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ctable%3E%20%3Ctbody%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2285%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22143%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOctober%2024%2C%202018%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22141%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOctober%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2285%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChange%20(in%20%25)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2285%5C%22%3ENifty-50%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ct