%20Battle%20of%20Tsushima%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6539381a0487ff031cadf7ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22879%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20battleship%20Oriol%20at%20a%20Japanese%20naval%20shipyard%20after%20it%20was%20surrendered%20following%20the%20Battle%20of%20Tsushima%20in%20May%201905.%3Cp%3ERussian%20and%20Soviet%20photo%20archive%20via%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20grueling%20and%20accident-prone%20seven-month%2C%2018%2C000-mile%20journey%2C%20the%20squadron%20reached%20the%20Tsushima%20Strait%20between%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20on%20May%2027%2C%201905%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-russian-navy-losses-against-ukraine-century-after-tsushima-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Japanese%20promptly%20obliterated%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-one%20Russian%20ships%20were%20sunk%20or%20scuttled%20and%20seven%20more%20were%20captured.%20Only%20three%20ships%20reached%20Vladivostok%2C%20though%20six%20others%20made%20it%20to%20neutral%20ports%20in%20China%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20and%20Madagascar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%205%2C000%20Russians%20sailors%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%206%2C000%20were%20captured.%20Japan%20lost%20only%20three%20torpedo%20boats%2C%20as%20well%20as%20117%20sailors%20killed%20and%20about%20500%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221603%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russia%20navy%20cruiser%20Oleg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6539353c96f7540cd0654308%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221202%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20cruiser%20Oleg%2C%20with%20damage%20from%20the%20Battle%20of%20Tsushima%2C%20in%20Manila%20Bay%20in%20June%201905.%3Cp%3ECollection%20of%20P.H.%20Proctor%20via%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BT