%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20China%20today%20are%20not%20the%20Russia%20and%20Japan%20of%20118%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20the%20US%20military%20faces%20circumstances%20distinct%20from%20those%20that%20confronted%20Russia%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20the%20Battle%20of%20Tsushima%20had%20far-reaching%20consequences%20that%20are%20still%20relevant%20now%2C%20Kendall%20argued%20in%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20major%20power%2C%20Russia%2C%20lost%20its%20influence%20in%20Asia.%20A%20major%20power%2C%20again%20Russia%2C%20saw%20its%20military%20credibility%20evaporate%2C%26quot%3B%20Kendall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20of%20the%20battle%20%26quot%3Bamplified%26quot%3B%20the%20arms%20race%20between%20Britain%20and%20Germany%20and%20fed%20a%20perception%20in%20Imperial%20Germany%20that%20Russia%20was%20weak%20and%20could%20be%20dealt%20with%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20conflict%2C%20leading%20the%20Germans%20to%20feel%20%26quot%3Bcomfortable%26quot%3B%20entering%20a%20two-front%20war%20nine%20years%20later%2C%20Kendall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221613%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20China%20risky%20intercept%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652fcc0b211def8ed837e99d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22916%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Chinese%20fighter%20jet%20conducting%20%26quot%3Ba%20coercive%20and%20risky%26quot%3B%20intercept%20of%20a%20US%20aircraft%20over%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20in%20June%202022.%3Cp%3EUS%20Defense%20Department%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20navy%2C%20which%20never%20truly%20recovered%2C%20experienced%20several%20mutinies%20in%20the%20following%20years%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bhelped%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20the%20Russian%20Revolution%20in%201917%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%26quot%3B%20Kendall%20said.%20In%20Asia%2C%20a%20rising%20Japan%20%26quot%3Bgained%20the%20confidence%20t