h%20for%20query%26quot%3B%20controversy.%20The%20committee%20agreed%20the%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20nearly%20three-hour-long%20proceeding%20today%2C%20the%20committee%20heard%20both%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20and%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20and%20discussed%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20allegations%20they%20have%20made%20against%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ethics%20committee%20chairman%20Vinod%20Sonkar%20told%20reporters%20they%20have%20sent%20letters%20to%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Ministry%20and%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20seeking%20details%20on%20key%20aspects%20of%20the%20case%20for%20a%20deeper%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20heard%20the%20lawyer%20and%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20ji.%20Taking%20note%20of%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20allegations%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20summon%20Mahua%20Moitra%20on%20Tuesday.%20She%20should%20come%20and%20present%20her%20side%20of%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sonkar%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20ethics%20committee%20proceeding%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dehadrai%2C%20on%20whose%20complaint%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20the%20entire%20case%20rests%2C%20was%20cross-examined%20by%20the%20ethics%20committee%2C%20while%20Mr%20Dubey%20was%20allowed%20to%20explain%20his%20allegations%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20CBI%20complaint%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20had%20written%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20levelled%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%20The%20Trinamool%20MP%20has%20called%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20her%20%26quot%3Bjilted%20ex%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20claimed%20to%20share%20%26quot%3Birrefutable%20evidence%26quot%3B%20of%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20giving%20bribes%20to%20Ms%20Moitra%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament.%20The%20questions%20were%20allegedly%20designed%20to%20target%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ethics%20committee%20will%20give%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20%26quot%3Bas%20early%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%2C%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20NDTV%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Pawan%20Bansal%20committee%20that%20gave%20its%20report%20in%20just%20two%20weeks%20in%20December%202005%20in%20the%20infamous%20cash-for-questions%20scam%20when%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dehadrai%20told%20reporters%20the%20proceedings%20were%20%26quot%3Bcordial%20and%20pleasant%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20answered%20all%20the%20questions%20the%20ethics%20committee%20asked.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20very%20cordial%20and%20they%20were%20very%20pleasant.%20Some%20questions%20were%20put%20to%20me%20and%20I%20have%20answered%20those%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20leaving.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey%20said%20he%20will%20be%20available%20whenever%20the%20ethics%20committee%20calls%20him.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20normal%20questions...%20All%20I%20can%20say%20is%20the%20MPs%20are%20concerned.%20When%20they%20call%20me%20next%20I%20will%20come.%20The%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20propriety%20and%20dignity%20of%20parliament%20will%20hold.%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20the%20dignity%20of%20parliament.%20The%20ethics%20committee%20is%20more%20worried%20than%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dubey%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20affidavit%2C%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20alleged%20the%20Trinamool%20MP%20shared%20her%20MP%20email%20so%20that%20he%20could%20send%20her%20information%20and%20she%20could%20raise%20the%20questions%20in%20parliament.%20He%20alleged%20she%20later%20gave%20him%20her%20parliament%20login%20and%20password%20for%20him%20to%20post%20the%20questions%20directly.%20The%20ethics%20committee%20rea