seat%20of%20Patan%2C%20where%20he%20would%20be%20facing%20off%20against%20his%20nephew%20Vijay%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELate%20Congress%20leader%20Mahendra%20Karma%E2%80%99s%20son%20Chavindra%20Karma%20will%20be%20fielded%20in%20Dantewada%2C%20where%20his%20mother%20Devaki%20Karma%20is%20the%20sitting%20MLA.%20Arun%20Vora%2C%20son%20of%20Motilal%20Vora%2C%20also%20got%20a%20ticket%20from%20Durg%20City%2C%20as%20did%20Pankaj%20Sharma%2C%20son%20of%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20Satyanarayan%20Sharma%2C%20from%20Raipur%20Rural.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20dark%20horse%20in%20the%20first%20list%20was%20Girish%20Dewangan%2C%20a%20close%20aide%20to%20CM%20Baghel.%20Dewangan%2C%20the%20sole%20candidate%20from%20the%20Dewangan%20community%20for%20the%20party%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Rajnandgaon%20against%20BJP%20stalwart%20and%20ex-CM%20Raman%20Singh.%20According%20to%20political%20commentators%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Baghel%20has%20a%20personal%20stake%20in%20Dewangan%E2%80%99s%20contest%20against%20Raman%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%2090%20seats%2C%2033%20seats%20are%20reserved%20for%20candidates%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%2010%20seats%20for%20candidates%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20In%20the%2047%20unreserved%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20fielded%2029%20OBC%20candidates.%20There%20are%2017%20women%20candidates%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20including%20five%20sitting%20MLAs%2C%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20and%20a%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2022%20sitting%20Congress%20MLAs%20who%20were%20denied%20tickets%2C%20at%20least%20five%20have%20lost%20their%20tickets%20to%20internal%20turmoil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-chhattisgarh-party-chief-deepak-baij-interview-elections%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Congress%20Giving%20Tickets%20to%20Winning%20Candidates%2C%E2%80%99%20Says%20Chhattisgarh%20Party%20Chief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ramanujganj%20MLA%20Brihaspti%20Singh%20and%20Samri%20MLA%20Chintamani%20Maharaj%20were%20done%20in%20by%20negative%20survey%20reports%2C%20Khujji%20MLA%20Chhanni%20Sahu%20seems%20to%20be%20paying%20a%20price%20for%20taking%20a%20stand%20against%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESahu%2C%20a%20first-time%20MLA%2C%20used%20to%20be%20a%20MNREGA%20worker.%20Before%20getting%20into%20active%20politics%2C%20Sahu%20used%20to%20construct%20mud%20houses%20in%20her%20village%20along%20with%20her%20father-in-law.%20A%20strong%20and%20vociferous%20leader%2C%20she%20was%20the%20only%20Congress%20leader%20who%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Adani-operated%20Parsa%20coal%20blocks%20in%20the%20state%20after%20the%20election.%20The%20Parsa%20coal%20block%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Hasdeo%20coal%20fields%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20blocks%20over%20which%20tribals%20in%20Hasdeo%20Aranya%20have%20been%20protesting%20for%20close%20to%20two%20years.%20According%20to%20tribals%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20no-objection%20certificate%20obtained%20by%20the%20government%20from%20the%20gram%20panchayat%20is%20from%20a%20fake%20proceeding%2C%20a%20claim%20rejected%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESahu%2C%20who%20raised%20the%20issue%20against%20her%20own%20government%2C%20has%20had%20her%20fair%20share%20of%20run-ins%20with%20the%20government%20machinery.%20She%20shot%20to%20public%20attention%20in%20March%202022%2C%20after%20she%20travelled%20over%20140%20km%20from%20Khujji%20to%20Raipur%20on%20her%20scooter%20to%20attend%20the%20assembly%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20after%20a%20spat%20with%20a%20truck%20driver%20over%20illegal%20sand%20mining%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20her%20husband%20Chandu%20Sahu%2C%20who%20was%20later%20arrested.%20Exasperated%20with%20the%20incident%2C%20in%20February%202022%2C%20Sahu%20returned%20her%20security%20detail%20and%20the%20government%20vehicle%20assigned%20to%20her%20despite%20coming%20from%20a%20Maoist-affected%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20leaving%20my%20husband%20here%20for%20questioning%2C%20the%20police%20can%20do%20whatever%20they%20want.%20If%20my%20PSO%20and%20driver%20were%20not%20even%20allowed%20to%20give%20their%20statements%20in%20the%20investigation%20of%20this%20case%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20how%20they%20are%20protecting%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20had%20told%20the%20press%20then%2C%20before%20whizzing%20off%20on%20her%20Honda%20scooter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20within%20the%20party%20believe%20Sahu%E2%80%99s%20outspokenness%20had%20led%20to%20discomfort%20in%20the%20party%20leadership%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself.%20She%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20MLAs%20who%20went%20to%20Delhi%20with%20Baghel%20in%20August%202021.%20Considered%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20Sahu%20held%20her%20ground%2C%20sources%20close%20to%20her%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20convert%20her%20to%20his%20camp%2C%20Baghel%20was%20wary%20of%20her.%20Her%20making%20news%20by%20deciding%20to%20ride%20around%20on%20a%20scooter%20gave%20her%20a%20rebel%20tag%20within%20the%20party%20even%20though%20she%20had%20a%20good%20hold%20of%20her%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParty%20insiders%20say%20Sahu%20was%20not%20given%20a%20ticket%20because%20several%20private%20surveys%2C%20other%20than%20the%20one%20conducted%20by%20AICC%2C%20showed%20her%20work%20in%20poor%20light.%20But%20for%20the%20MLA%2C%20the%20decision%20was%20a%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20raised%20a%20single%20issue%20for%20personal%20gain%20in%20my%20past%20five%20years.%20I%20have%20worked%20diligently%20and%20followed%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20the%20party.%20If%20even%20that%20gets%20me%20negative%20results%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20criteria%20is%20being%20followed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26150631%2FF7fi_0PXwAA3SUA.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22991%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26150631%2FF7fi_0PXwAA3SUA.jpeg%20991w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26150631%2FF7fi_0PXwAA3SUA-300x174.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChhanni%20Sahu.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40chhanni_sahu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20has%20fielded%20Bhola%20Ram%20Sahu%2C%20the%20erstwhile%20Congress%20MLA%20before%20Chhanni%20was%20given%20a%20ticket%20in%202018.%20Bhola%20Ram%2C%20who%20has%20some%20experience%20of%20being%20left%20high%20and%20dry%2C%20believes%20history%20is%20repeating.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20sitting%20MLA%20when%20my%20ticket%20was%20cut%20and%20Chhanni%20ji%20was%20given%20a%20ticket.%20Now%2C%20the%20party%20wants%20some%20change%2C%20so%20I%20am%20back.%20The%20aim%20is%20for%20Congress%20to%20win%20the%20election%2C%20whoever%20is%20the%20candidate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Bhola%20Ram%20not%20only%20has%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Geeta%20Sahu%C2%A0but%20also%20establish%20a%20working%20relationship%20with%20Chhanni.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20within%20the%20party%20agree%20that%20Chhanni%20Sahu%20was%20a%20pawn%20in%20the%20larger%20game%20of%20internal%20politics%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Chhattisgarh%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20list%20of%20candidates%2C%20two%20leaders%20who%20were%20at%20a%20crossroads%20with%20Singh%20Deo%20were%20missing.%20Ramanujganj%20MLA%20Brihaspati%20Singh%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20Ambikapur%20mayor%20Ajay%20Tirkey.%20While%20Tirkey%20has%20been%20a%20crowd%20favourite%20with%20many%20laurels%20to%20his%20credit%2C%20Singh%20was%20unceremoniously%20dumped.%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Findia%2Fchhattisgarh-fight-between-dy-cm-ts-singh-deo-mla-brihaspati-singh-escalates%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBalrampur%252C%2520Brihaspati%2520Singh.-%2CDuring%2520a%2520mass%2520meeting%2520in%2520Balrampur%252DRamanujganj%252C%2520Singh%2520Deo%2520openly%2Cwhile%2520addressing%2520the%2520public%2520gathering.%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20Singh%20Deo%20of%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20him%20in%202021.%20The%20MLA%20gave%20a%20press%20statement%20and%20then%20the%20issue%20was%20raised%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20prompting%20a%20walk-out%20by%20Singh%20Deo.%20While%20Brihaspati%20Singh%20later%20apologised%2C%20Singh%20Deo%20neither%20forgave%20nor%20forgot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20while%20holding%20a%20mass%20meeting%20in%20the%20area%2C%20without%20taking%20any%20names%2C%20Singh%20Deo%20said%20that%20any%20sleight%20against%20him%20or%20his%20parents%20would%20not%20be%20tolerated.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20accused%20of%20plotting%20a%20murder.%20Allegations%20were%20levelled%20against%20me%2C%20my%20parents%20and%20my%20family.%20The%20party%20can%20decide%20what%20will%20happen%20here%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20compromise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20seat%20falls%20in%20the%20Ambikapur%20region%2C%20a%20Singh%20Deo%20stronghold%2C%20the%20party%20clearly%20decided%20to%20follow%20his%20lead%20and%20Brihaspati%20was%20promptly%20denied%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESamri%20MLA%20Chintamani%20Maharaj%20was%20once%20believed%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Singh%20Deo%20but%20later%20shifted%20camps.%20He%20was%20also%20denied%20a%20ticket.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20massive%20opposition%20to%20Chintamani%20in%20Samri.%20The%20BJP%20led%20a%20strong%20anti-corruption%20campaign%20against%20him.%20Hence%20a%20new%20face%20has%20been%20fielded%2C%E2%80%9D%20party%20insiders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26150620%2FF4YVORmWYAE9Czf.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26150620%2FF4YVORmWYAE9Czf.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26150620%2FF4YVORmWYAE9Czf-300x164.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26150620%2FF4YVORmWYAE9Czf-1024x558.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681837%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ET.S.%20Singh%20Deo.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40TS_SinghDeo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EFacing%20the%20prospect%20of%20rebellions%20by%20MLAs%20who%20have%20been%20denied%20tickets%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20focusing%20on%20pacifying%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%20is%20not%20treating%20anyone%20unfairly.%20A%20lot%20of%20research%20has%20gone%20into%20making%20these%20decisions.%20For%20those%20who%20worked%20well%20but%20have%20not%20been%20fielded%20again%2C%20it%20is%20because%20the%20party%20wants%20to%20give%20greater%20responsibility%20to%20them.%20Everyone%20will%20be%20treated%20based%20on%20their%20work%20and%20will%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20work%20for%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20leader%20from%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Kanker%20MLA%20Anoop%20Nag%20who%20was%20denied%20a%20ticket%20became%20the%20first%20Congress%20MLA%20to%20declare%20his%20intentions%20of%20running%20independently.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20filed%20my%20nomination%20as%20an