e%2C%20it%20was%20virtually%20a%20tie.%20The%20menu%20prices%20were%20nearly%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Note%3A%20Some%20items%20were%20not%20available%20in%20the%20same%20quantity.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20bought%20five%20pieces%20of%20chicken%20tenders%20at%20Popeyes.%20I%20could%20only%20buy%20six%20pieces%20at%20KFC.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Popeyes%2C%20five%20pieces%20of%20chicken%20tenders%20cost%20%247.49.%20Six%20pieces%20of%20chicken%20tenders%20at%20KFC%20cost%20%249.99.%20The%20cost%20reflects%20a%20la%20carte%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20KFC%2C%20a%20four-piece%20fried%20chicken%20combo%20meal%20with%20mashed%20potatoes%20and%20a%20biscuit%20cost%20%2412.69.%20At%20Popeyes%2C%20a%20four-piece%20combo%20with%20mashed%20potatoes%20and%20a%20biscuit%20cost%20%2413.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20classic%20chicken%20sandwich%20at%20Popeyes%20was%20%245.49.%20The%20same%20sandwich%20at%20KFC%20was%20%245.29.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKFC%20took%20about%203%20minutes%20to%20prepare%20my%20order%2C%20while%20Popeyes%20took%20about%207%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Popeyes%20tenders%20had%20a%20light%2C%20flaky%20breading%20%E2%80%93%20almost%20like%20a%20tempura-style%20coating.%20Steam%20was%20coming%20off%20the%20chicken%20on%20my%20first%20bite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Popeyes%20chicken%20tenders%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653857110487ff031cad7306%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Popeyes%20chicken%20tenders%20had%20a%20thin%20tempura-style%20coating.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Popeyes%20tenders%20were%20a%20decent%20size.%20They%20looked%20longer%20and%20more%20slender%20than%20a%20tender%20at%20Raising%20Cane's.%20I%20ordered%20the%20mild%20version.%20It%20was%20fairly%20hot%20to%20the%20touch%2C%20indicating%20it%20was%20freshly%20cooked.%20The%20chicken%20was%20tender%20and%20juicy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20icing%20on%20the%20cake%20at%20Popeyes%20was%20the%20dipping%20sauces.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Popeyes'%20dipping%20sauces%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653857b296f7540cd064bdd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20loved%20the%20innovative%20dipping%20sauces%20at%20Popeyes%2C%20especially%20the%20Blackened%20Ranch.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPopeyes%20has%20a%20collection%20of%20innovative%20and%20tempting%20dipping%20sauces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20especially%20impressed%20with%20the%20Mardi%20Gras%20Mustard%20and%20the%20Blackened%20Ranch.%20Both%20were%20very%20tasty%20compared%20to%20the%20boring%20sauces%20I%20found%20at%20KFC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20unlike%20Chick-fil-A%2C%20where%20some%20stores%20charge%20for%20extra%20sauce%2C%20both%20KFC%20and%20Popeyes%20provide%20extra%20sauce%20at%20no%20extra%20cost.%20The%20employees%20at%20Popeyes%20were%20very%20friendly%20when%20I%20asked%20them%20if%20I%20could%20get%20more%20Blackened%20Ranch%20to%20take%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20KFC%2C%20the%20chicken%20tenders%20were%20thicker%20than%20at%20Popeyes%2C%20but%20the%20meat%20was%20bone%20dry.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KFC%20chicken%20tenders%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538584496f7540cd064bddb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKFC's%20chicken%20tenders%20were%20thicker%20compared%20to%20Popeyes'.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20breading%20on%20the%20KFC%20chicken%20tenders%20was%20thicker%20but%20less%20flaky%20than%20Popeyes'.%20And%2C%20while%20the%20tender%20had%20more%20girth%20than%20Popeyes'%2C%20I%20found%20the%20white%20chicken%20very%20dry%20and%20unappetizing.%20The%20chicken%20tenders%20at%20KFC%20were%20also%20greasier%20to%20the%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20suspect%20they%20were%20sitting%20under%20heat%20for%20a%20while.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20observed%20KFC%20workers%20preparing%20drive-thru%20and%20takeout%20meals%20from%20food%20sitting%20in%20preheated%20ovens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChicken%20tenders%20winner%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Popeyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20skin%20on%20Popeyes'%20bone-in%20fried%20chicken%20peeled%20off%20before%20I%20could%20take%20a%20proper%20bite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fried%20chicken%20from%20Popeyes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653859040487ff031cad7317%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fried%20chicken%20from%20Popeyes%20is%20served%20in%20a%20tray%20lined%20with%20branded%20paper.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20get%20a%20complete%20bite%20because%20the%20breading%20fell%20off%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20picked%20up%20a%20large%20piece%20of%20chicken.%20It%20was%20greasy%2C%20but%20not%20as%20sticky%20and%20messy%20as%20KFC's%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20using%20a%20spork%20to%20eat%20some%20of%20the%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20sporks%2C%20they're%20cute%20and%20versatile.%20But%20I'd%20prefer%20to%20have%20forks%2C%20spoons%20and%20knives%20as%20my%20cutlery.%20Are%20sporks%20a%20fried%20chicken%20chain%20tradition%20because%20KFC%20also%20had%20sporks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKFC's%20fried%20chicken%20didn't%20live%20up%20to%20its%20finger-lickin'%20good%20reputation.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KFC%20FRIED%20CHICKEN%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65385b70356802a56be2f1b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKFC's%20fried%20chicken%20was%20super%20greasy.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20mild%20fried%20chicken%20at%20Popeyes%20and%20compared%20it%20to%20KFC's%20original%20recipe%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expected%20to%20be%20dazzled%20by%20KFC's%20chicken.%20The%20breading%20on%20the%20skin%20was%20darker%20than%20Popeyes'%2C%20giving%20me%20the%20impression%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20get%20a%20very%20seasoned%20crunchy%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chicken%20was%20juicy%20but%20also%20very%20greasy.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20couldn't%20eat%20any%20more%20because%20my%20chicken%20kept%20slipping%20through%20my%20fingers%20as%20my%20hands%20were%20lathered%20in%20oil.%20I%20needed%20a%20Wet%20Nap%20towelette%20between%20bites.%20When%20I%20returned%20home%2C%20I%20felt%20bloated%20and%20had%20to%20take%20two%20chewable%20Tums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20expected%20the%20KFC%20biscuit%20and%20mashed%20potatoes%20to%20top%20Popeyes'.%20I%20was%20totally%20wrong.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KFC%20versus%20Popeyes%20mashed%20potatoes%20and%20biscuit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65385aa296f7540cd064be0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20KFC%20biscuit%2C%20left%2C%20looked%20deformed.%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20peppery%20gravy%20at%20Popeyes.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biscuit%20at%20Popeyes%20was%20buttery%20and%20flaky%20on%20the%20inside.%20It%20was%20a%20solid%20Southern-style%20biscuit%2C%20while%20the%20KFC%20biscuit%20looked%20like%20a%20deformed%20puck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KFC%20biscuit%20was%20also%20spongy%20instead%20of%20flaky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Popeyes%20mashed%20potatoes%20were%20super%20creamy%20and%20served%20with%20a%20light%20serving%20of%20peppery%20gravy.%20It%20was%20like%20eating%20Thanksgiving%20mashed%20potatoes%20but%20with%20a%20spicy%20kick%20to%20the%20gravy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKFC's%20mashed%20potatoes%20were%20swimming%20in%20gravy.%20The%20potatoes%20were%20creamy%20but%20tasted%20like%20they%20came%20from%20frozen-dinner%20meals%20bought%20at%20the%20grocery%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFried%20chicken%20winner%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPopeyes.%20The%20sides%20at%20Popeyes%20helped%20the%20chain%20edge%20out%20KFC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Popeyes%20chicken%20sandwich%20is%20a%20work%20of%20culinary%20art.%20I%20can%20see%20why%20it%20launched%20the%20chicken%20sandwich%20wars%20of%202019.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Popeyes%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65385c6696f7540cd064be54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20loved%20the%20spongy%20bun%20that%20clung%20to%20the%20chicken%20breast.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopeyes-chicken-sandwich-fast-food-menu-item-of-2019-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edebuted%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Popeyes%20chicken%20sandwich%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20a%20social%20media%20sensation.%20Stores%20ran%20out%20of%20supplies%20as%20fans%20went%20bonkers%20for%20the%20chicken%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buzz%20over%20the%20sandwich%20even%20rattled%20the%20reigning%20fried%20chicken%20champ%2C%20Chick-fil-A.%20The%20Atlanta-based%20chain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopeyes-chicken-sandwich-rise-and-fall-story-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eignited%20a%20social%20media%20spat%20with%20Popeyes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20led%20to%20the%20chicken%20sandwich%20wars%20of%202019.%20Copycat%20chicken%20sandwiches%20began%20popping%20up%20on%20m