%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fevery-states-official-state-bird-2018-12%5C%22%3Erobin%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20a%20fossil%20from%20a%20Pinacosaurus%20grangeri%2C%20paleontologists%20think%20that%20some%20large%20dinosaurs%20might%20have%20chirped%20like%20birds%2C%20not%20roared%20like%20lions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fossil%20is%20the%20first%20intact%20larynx%20bone%20from%20a%20dinosaur%20ever%20found%2C%20the%20scientists%20said%20in%20their%20study%20which%20was%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Db12ffb056f447d903a2369f0c8f9a579929f3b99d3950ebcf1bc2a64bd41e809%26postID%3D65381e0dcf767c5e2eb273d1%26postSlug%3Ddinosaurs-chirped-like-birds-suggests-ancient-throat-bone-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs42003-023-04513-x%5C%22%3ENature%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bunique%20and%20beautiful%26quot%3B%20specimen%20is%20part%20of%20a%20voice%20box%2C%20Junki%20Yoshida%2C%20a%20paleontologist%20at%20Hokkaido%20University%20Museum%20in%20Japan%20who%20led%20the%20research%2C%20said%20in%20a%20presentation%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-american-museum-of-natural-history-2015-9%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20they%20found%20the%20bone%20and%20discovered%20its%20purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20actual%20image%20of%20the%20dinosaur%20larynx%20next%20to%20scanned%20recreations%20of%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65392eb396f7540cd0653251%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20scan%20of%20the%20fossilized%20larynx%20of%20the%20Ankylosaurus%20dinosaur%20Pinacosaurus%20grangeri.%3Cp%3EMichael%20D%E2%80%99Emic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20small%