ircumstances%20of%2C%20I%20suppose%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20wickets%20probably%20changed%20the%20way%20I%20would%20have%20gone%20about%20it%20if%20it%20was%20just%20me%20and%20Davey%20at%20the%20back%20end.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20just%20super%20selective.%20Even%20with%20the%20boundaries%20I%20was%20hitting%2C%20until%20I%20got%20to%20about%2050%20or%2060%2C%20I%20was%20literally%20hitting%20them%20flat%20through%20the%20gap%20or%20picking%20my%20spots%20pretty%20clearly%20where%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20and%20it%20was%20only%20the%20back%20end%20where%20I%20tried%20to%20just%20pump%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Maxwell%C2%A0said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20talking%20about%20the%20inning%20against%20Netherlands%2C%C2%A0Maxwell%C2%A0said%20that%20he%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20games%20in%20India%20which%20helped%20him%20to%20score%20the%20fastest%20century%20at%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20he%20is%20not%20too%20worried%20about%20people%20saying%20that%20he%20hasn't%20made%20runs%20in%20ODI%20cricket%20because%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0With%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698311340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ftgrcktq8_glenn-maxwell_625x300_26_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fi-took-40-balls-to-get-off-the-mark-glenn-maxwell-hit-a-ton-sunil-gavaskars-ultimate-tribute-on-fiery-cricket-world-cup-knock-4514179%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cricket%20World%20Cup%3A%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20hit%20some%20improbable-looking%20shots%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20only%20he%20is%20capable%20off%20for%20on%20way%20to%20hitting%20a%2040-ball%20ton%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fi-took-40-balls-to-get-off-the-mark-glenn-maxwell-hit-a-ton-sunil-gavaskars-ultimate-tribute-on-fiery-cricket-world-cup-knock-4514179%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fi-took-40-balls-to-get-off-the-mark-glenn-maxwell-hit-a-ton-sunil-gavaskars-ultimate-tribute-on-fiery-cricket-world-cup-knock-4514179%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fi-took-40-balls-to-get-off-the-mark-glenn-maxwell-hit-a-ton-sunil-gavaskars-ultimate-tribute-on-fiery-cricket-world-cup-knock-4514179%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Banner%20At%20Congress%20Office%20Says%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20'2024%20PM'%2C%20Key%20Ally%20Slams%20Move%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20banner%20describing%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20'2024%20Prime%20Minister'%20appeared%20outside%20the%20Congress%20party%20office%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20days%20after%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20office%20put%20up%20a%20similar%20poster%20calling%20its%20party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20India's%20'future%20Prime%20Minister'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20banner%20also%20described%20its%20state%20president%20Ajay%20Rai%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20poster%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20state%20spokesperson%20Fakhrul%20Hasan%20'Chand'%20who%20had%20put%20up%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20poster%20said%20it%20was%20their%20party%20which%20was%20fighting%20the%20battle%20of%20backwards%2C%20Dalits%20and%20minorities%2C%20so%20it%20did%20not%20matter%20how%20many%20posters%20the%20Congress%20put%20up%20as%20people%20wanted%20Yadav%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20banner%20describing%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20as%20the%20'future%20Prime%20Minister'%20put%20up%20on%20Monday%20by%20a%20party%20worker%20generated%20a%20buzz%20in%20political%20circles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20described%20it%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMungeri%20Lal%20ke%20haseen%20sapne%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20pipedream)%26quot%3B%20of%20Yadav's%20associates%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20other%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20opposition%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20hoarding%20put%20up%20by%20party%20worker%20Nitant%20Singh%20Nitin%20carries%20the%20pictures%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Ajay%20Rai%20with%20the%20slogan%20%26quot%3B2024%20mein%20Rahul%2C%202027%20mein%20Rai%2C%20desh-pradesh%20bol%20raha%20hai%2C%20haath%20ke%20saath%20aayen%26quot%3B%20(Rahul%20in%202024%2C%20(Ajay)%20Rai%20in%202027%2C%20both%20country%20and%20state%20are%20asking%20you%20to%20come%20in%20support%20of%20the%20hand%20(Congress%20symbol)).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitin%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20banner%2C%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20feeling%20of%20the%20party's%20workers.%20Also%2C%20the%20common%20people%20want%20to%20come%20along%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20a%20direct%20contest%20between%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Ajay%20Rai%20will%20become%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20state.%20There%20is%20growing%20confidence%20among%20the%20people%20towards%20our%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Nitin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Dwijendra%20Tripathi%20said%20the%20hoarding%20has%20been%20put%20up%20by%20a%20party%20worker%20and%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20what%20he%20and%20other%20workers%20feel.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20often%20seen%20in%20politics%2C%20it%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20party%20workers'%20feelings%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tripathi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20sharply%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20state%20spokesperson%20Hasan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBoth%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20the%20same%20and%20the%20Samajwadis%20have%20been%20saying%20this%20for%20long.%20Any%20party%20can%20put%20up%20posters%20as%20per%20their%20sentiment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20which%20is%20fighting%20the%20battle%20of%20backwards%2C%20Dalits%20and%20minorities.%20No%20matter%20how%20many%20posters%20Congress%20puts%20up%2C%20the%20public%20wants%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20to%20be%20the%20PM.%20When%20an%20SP%20chief%20becomes%20a%20PM%2C%20an%20SP%20leader%20will%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20UP.%20The%20vote%20share%20of%20Congress%20in%20UP%20is%20less%20than%20that%20of%20many%20regional%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hasan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20poster%20put%20up%20by%20Hasan%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BHearty%20congratulations%20and%20best%20wishes%20on%20his%20birthday%20to%20the%20future%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20country%2C%20respected%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20Mr%20Yadav's%20official%20date%20of%20birth%20is%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20publicly%20expressed%20his%20unhappiness%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20failure%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20had%20also%20referred%20to%20UPCC%20chief%20Ajay%20Rai%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bchirkut%26quot%3B%20(low-level)%20leader.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698311220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F2tvo7hf4_rahul-gandhi-2024-pm-banner-at-congress-office-ani_625x300_26_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbanner-at-congress-office-say-rahul-gandhi-2024-pm-key-ally-slams-move-4515242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20banner%20describing%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20'2024%20Prime%20Minister'%20appeared%20outside%20the%20Congress%20party%20office%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20da