20with%20other%20shady%20dealings%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20this%20regime%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-coal-imports-over-pricing-customers-overcharged-fuel-ft%5C%22%3Ecoal%20import%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20raked%20up%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20(FT)%20carries%20all%20the%20distinctive%20features%20of%20business%20conducted%20in%20a%20kleptocracy%2C%20a%20term%20that%20etymologically%20derives%20from%20the%20Greek%20for%20%E2%80%9Cthief%20rule%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20kleptocracy%20fosters%20unlimited%20grand%20corruption%2C%20ensuring%20near%20total%20impunity%20for%20those%20authorised%20to%20loot%20by%20the%20head%20of%20state%20and%20his%20minions.%20In%20a%20kleptocracy%2C%20illegal%20activities%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20cronies%20are%20ruled%20licit%20by%20a%20corrupted%20legal%20system.%20Other%20hallmarks%20of%20a%20kleptocracy%20are%20rent-seeking%20through%20awarding%20lucrative%20contracts%20to%20family%20members%20or%20friends%20and%20reframing%20the%20domestic%20narrative%20by%20capturing%20ownership%20of%20media%20companies.%20Does%20this%20ring%20a%20bell%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FT%E2%80%99s%20investigative%20analysis%20is%20a%20damning%20indictment%20of%20the%20regime.%20It%20alleges%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20has%20been%20inflating%20imported%20coal%20costs%20by%20using%20offshore%20middlemen%2C%20because%20of%20which%20the%20price%20of%20coal%20more%20than%20doubles%20on%20landing%2C%20and%20thereby%2C%20the%20Indian%20consumer%20is%20being%20duped%20into%20paying%20twice%20his%20legitimate%20dues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20jaw-droppingly%20significant%20is%20that%20this%20regime%20knew%20what%20was%20going%20on%20and%20did%20nothing%20to%20stop%20the%20bleeding.%20Also%2C%20consumers%20may%20have%20paid%20for%20inflated%20coal%20prices%20between%202019%20and%202021%20when%20the%20pandemic%20had%20already%20hit%20their%20incomes%20and%20savings%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20now%20one%20is%20not%20surprised%20at%20the%20unholy%20nexus%20between%20the%20corporates%20and%20this%20dispensation.%20The%20dubious%20Rafale%20deal%2C%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20dirt%2C%20the%20pricey%20airport%20and%20port%20contracts%2C%20et%20al%2C%20betray%20the%20lockstep%20between%20government%20and%20the%20most%20powerful%20business%20houses.%20More%20disturbing%20is%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20equivocal%2C%20if%20not%20complicit%2C%20stance%20on%20these%20critical%20matters%20of%20integrity%20and%20ethics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20not%20what%20the%20country%20bargained%20for%20when%20this%20regime%20first%20took%20up%20the%20reins%20almost%20a%20decade%20ago.%20In%202014%2C%20Modi%20rode%20to%20power%20on%20the%20back%20of%20an%20anti-corruption%20wave%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20messianic%20India%20Against%20Corruption%20(IAC)%20movement%20that%20organised%20a%20nationwide%20stir%20against%20endemic%20political%20and%20bureaucratic%20corruption%20and%20brought%20the%20jittery%2C%20dishonest%20UPA%20government%20down%20to%20its%20knees.%20In%20those%20heady%20days%20of%20fanciful%20idealism%2C%20we%20%E2%80%93%20the%20gullible%20fools%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20passionately%20believed%20that%20the%20potent%20Lokpal%20Act%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20accession%20would%20clean%20the%20Augean%20stables.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Strategy%20Lies%20in%20the%20Constant%20Use%20of%20Self-Image%20in%20the%20Religious%20Context%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-self-image-religion-politics-image%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Strategy%20Lies%20in%20the%20Constant%20Use%20of%20Self-Image%20in%20the%20Religious%20Context%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20towering%2C%20squeaky-clean%20persona%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20amplified%20by%20mobilising%20every%20possible%20propaganda%20tool%2C%20ensured%20that%20corruption%20as%20an%20issue%20of%20public%20concern%20dropped%20off%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20radar.%20His%20spurious%20public%20image%20of%20personal%20integrity%20for%20long%20subsumed%20criticism%20of%20corruption%20in%20his%20government.%20A%20credulous%20public%20was%20convinced%20that%20this%20superman%20had%20resolved%20the%20problem%20of%20corruption.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENa%20khaunga%20na%20khaane%20dhunga%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20beguiling%20catchphrase%20that%20calmed%20a%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpen%20democratic%20societies%20with%20free%20access%20to%20information%20are%20vital%20for%20fighting%20corruption.%20The%20most%20important%20outcome%20of%20transparency%20is%20that%20it%20has%20a%20civilising%20effect%20on%20political%20behaviour%20through%20democratic%20accountability.%20In%20fact%2C%20social%20thinkers%20contend%20that%20transparency%20and%20free%20flow%20of%20information%20contribute%20to%20regime%20effectiveness%20in%20matters%20ranging%20from%20development%20and%20growth%20to%20social%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20kleptocratic%20mode%20of%20governance%20can%20thrive%20only%20in%20an%20authoritarian%20and%20opaque%20milieu.%20This%20government%20has%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20an%20intimidatory%20environment%20of%20%E2%80%9Cshock%20and%20awe%E2%80%9D%20which%20has%20virtually%20terrorised%20every%20institution%20into%20toeing%20its%20line.%20A%20nameless%20fear%20has%20gripped%20government%20offices%20as%20the%20bureaucracy%20cowers%20behind%20the%20%E2%80%98steel%20frame%E2%80%99%20in%20an%20ecosystem%20where%20loyalty%20to%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20is%20paramount%20and%20not%20impartiality%20and%20probity.%20Nobody%20dares%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%20or%20challenge%20faulty%20government%20policies.%20This%20has%20had%20a%20terribly%20deleterious%20effect%20on%20the%20fight%20against%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20deadlier%20for%20the%20future%20because%20of%20its%20long-term%20impact%20has%20been%20the%20well%20thought%20out%2C%20methodical%20positioning%20of%20individuals%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20ideological%20bent%E2%80%9D%20in%20critical%20government%20institutions%20including%20the%20UPSC%2C%20CAG%2C%20UGC%20and%20JNU.%20The%20sentinels%20of%20Hindutva%20have%20been%20planted%20everywhere.%20And%20those%2C%20like%20the%20intrepid%20professor%20K.S.%20James%2C%20director%20of%20the%20International%20Institute%20of%20Population%20Sciences%20(IIPS)%2C%20who%20refuse%20to%20bend%20but%20say%20it%20like%20it%20is%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-iips-director-resignation-nfhs-health-ministry%5C%22%3Eare%20booted%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20most%20institutions%20have%20become%20grovelling%20propagandists%20of%20the%20political%20executive.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20what%20is%20expected%20of%20every%20public%20functionary%2C%20and%20the%20government%20makes%20no%20bones%20about%20it.%20Setting%20aside%20all%20principles%2C%20the%20government%20has%20decided%20that%20its%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3Ewill%20act%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Erath%20prabharis%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20spread%20information%20on%20the%20alleged%20achievements%20of%20the%20government.%20A%20similar%20diktat%20was%20earlier%20issued%20to%20the%20armed%20forces%20personnel%20proceeding%20on%20leave.%20Sycophancy%20is%20now%20an%20ordained%20public%20duty.%20Clearly%2C%20this%20government%20is%20bent%20on%20corrupting%20our%20souls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20oppressive%20environment%2C%20the%20institutions%20meant%20to%20combat%20corruption%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20mere%20ciphers.%20The%20calculated%20diminution%20of%20the%20Lokpal%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%20Although%20the%20Lokpal%20and%20Lokayuktas%20Act%20was%20enacted%20in%202013%2C%20this%20government%20with%20impunity%20deferred%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20Lokpal%20by%20more%20than%20five%20years%20until%202019%2C%20in%20the%20meantime%20subverting%20the%20statute%20with%20critical%20amendments%20that%20diluted%20the%20powers%20and%20reach%20of%20the%20Lokpal.%20Predictably%2C%20only%20those%20well-disposed%20towards%20the%20government%20occupy%20the%20top%20posts%20in%20the%20supreme%20body%20ordained%20to%20fight%20corruption%20in%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20%E2%80%98Double%20Engine%E2%80%99%20is%20Pass%C3%A9%2C%20Hereafter%20Modi-Shah%20Will%20Pick%20or%20Junk%20BJP%20CMs%20at%20Will%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdouble-engine-bjp-modi-shah%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Double%20Engine%E2%80%99%20is%20Pass%C3%A9%2C%20Hereafter%20Modi-Shah%20Will%20Pick%20or%20Junk%20BJP%20CMs%20at%20Will%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20extant%20provisions%20in%20the%20Lokpal%20Act%20have%20been%20disregarded.%20The%20Act%20envisages%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20CBI%20to%20the%20Investigation%20and%20Prosecution%20wings%20of%20the%20Lokpal%2C%20but%20that%2C%20we%20know%20for%20sure%2C%20will%20not%20happen%20so%20long%20as%20Modi%20is%20around.%20Instead%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccaged%20parrot%E2%80%9D%20has%20transmuted%20into%20a%20deadly%20force%20that%20is%20being%20used%20to%20settle%20scores%20with%20the%20opponents%20of%20the%20regime.%20We%20have%20a%20Lokpal%20alright%2C%20but%20one%20that%20is%20innocuous%20and%20a%20pale%20shadow%20of%20the%20ombudsman%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20had%20rooted%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEqually%20worrying%20is%20the%20systematic%20undermining%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20law%20which%20is%20aimed%20at%20tearing%20down%20the%20wall%20of%20bureaucratic%20secrecy%20behind%20which%20governments%20do%20their%20dirty%20work.%20Fortified%20by%20this%20government%E2%80%99s%20imprimatur%20of%20opacity%20in%20governance%2C%20major%20public%20organisations%20are%20guilty%20of%20routinely%20withholding%20information%20on%20matters%20of%20public%20interest.%20By%20far%20the%20most%20infamous%20instance%20is%20the%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20comply%20with%20an%20RTI%20application%20seeking%20to%20verify%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20BA%20degree%20and%20despite%20the%20chief%20information%20commissioner%20directing%20the%20university%20to%20disclose%20the%20information.%20(Even%20more%20surreal%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20courts%20have%20upheld%20the%20non-disclosure%20of%20our%20leading%20public%20functionary%E2%80%99s%20academic%20credentials.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20entire%20media%20focus%20on%20the%20venality%20and%20depredations%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20other%20opponents%20of%20the%20regime%2C%20the%20everyday%2C%20all-pervasive%20corruption%20faced%20by%20the%20ordinary%20citizen%20is%20dismissed%20as%20a%20piffling%20problem%20that%20we%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20in%20our%20stride.%20According%20to%20the%20Global%20Corruption%20Barometer%20(GCB)%20compiled%20by%20Transparency%20International%20in%20November%202020%2C%20India%20has%20the%20dubious%20distinction%20of%20the%20highest%20bribery%20rate%20(39%25)%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20greatest%20number%20of%20people%20who%20use%20personal%20connections%20to%20access%20public%20services%20(46%25).%20Most%20respondents%20(89%25)%20felt%20that%20corruption%20in%20government%20is%20the%20main%20problem.%20A%20large%20number%20(63%25)%20think%20that%20reporting%20corruption%20would%20invite%20retaliation.%20India%20languishes%20at%2086th%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20in%20the%202022%20Corruption%20Perception%20Index%20with%20a%20score%20of%2040%20which%20is%20worse%20than%20the%20global%20average%20score%20of%2043.%20Clearly%2C%20%E2%80%9Cna%20khaunga%2C%20na%20khaane%20dhunga%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20cruel%20joke%20played%20on%20the%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20see%20today%20is%20not%20only%20corruption%20by%20individuals%20but%20wholesale%2C%20across%20the%20board%20subornation%20of%20systems%20and%20institutions.%20At%20a%20metaphysical%20level%2C%20the%20frontal%20assault%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20secular%20India%20has%20corrupted%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20soul%20(a%20broken%20Manipur%20is%20the%20first%20casualty).%20And%20the%20greatest%20irony%20is%20that%2C%20perched%20atop%20the%20biggest%20scams%20in%20our%20history%20and%20a%20deeply%20unhappy%20and%20divided%20India%20of%20his%20making%2C%20the%20Vishwaguru%20still%20unabashedly%20claims%20to%20be%20leading%20the%20fight%20against%20corruption%2C%20repeatedly%20accusing%20the%20Opposition%20of%20fostering%20criminality%20and%20advising%20his%20puppets%20in%20the%20central%20probe%20agencies%20not%20to%20spare%20the%20corrupt.%20The%20hypocrisy%20is%20stunning!%20F.W.%20Robertson%20had%20people%20like%20the%20Vishwaguru%20in%20mind%20when%20he%20observed%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20three%20things%20in%20the%20world%20that%20deserves%20no%20mercy%20%E2%80%93%20hypocrisy%2C%20fraud%20and%20tyranny.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20The%20views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698310843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26142523%2FF8N0WYKXEAAQlm-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finarguably-the-most-corrupt-regime-ever%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20we%20see%20today%20is%20not%20only%20corruption%20by%20individuals%20but%20wholesale%2C%20across%20the%20board%20subornation%20of%20systems%20and%20institutions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finarguably-the-most-corrupt-regime-ever%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B