%20Union%20signed%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20to%20establish%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20corridor%20will%20encourage%20and%20provide%20impetus%20to%20economic%20development%20through%20enhanced%20connectivity%20and%20economic%20integration%20between%20Asia%2C%20West%20Asia%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Europe%2C%20as%20per%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%20will%20consist%20of%20two%20separate%20corridors%2C%20the%20East%20corridor%20connecting%20India%20to%20West%20Asia%2FMiddle%20East%20and%20the%20Northern%20corridor%20connecting%20West%20Asia%2FMiddle%20East%20to%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20include%20a%20rail%20line%2C%20which%20upon%20completion%2C%20will%20provide%20a%20reliable%20and%20cost-effective%20cross-border%20ship-to-rail%20transit%20network%20to%20supplement%20the%20existing%20multi-modal%20transport%20routes%20enhancing%20transhipment%20of%20goods%20and%20services%20between%20South%20East%20Asia%20through%20India%20to%20West%20Asia%2FMiddle%20East%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20recently%20lauded%20the%20corridor%20and%20said%20the%20project%20will%20spur%20opportunities%20for%20investment%20across%20two%20continents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20rail%20port%20project%20is%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20build%20a%20more%20sustainable%2C%20integrated%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20has%20entered%20its%2020th%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20said%20that%20his%20goal%20against%20the%20Hamas%20war%20is%20%26quot%3Bsaving%20the%20nation%26quot%3B%20and%20promised%20that%20a%20ground%20incursion%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20will%20start%20soon%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%20reported%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Israel%20is%20getting%20ready%20for%20a%20ground%20operati