rom%20Ongoing%20Protests%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20asked%20for%2030%20days%2C%20we%20gave%20you%2041%2C%20but%20nothing%20was%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patil%20told%20Mahajan.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20way%20we%20will%20call%20off%20the%20protest%2C%20as%20our%20youths%20are%20suffering.%20The%20government%20had%20promised%20that%20it%20would%20withdraw%20the%20cases%20against%20protesters%20after%20the%20September%201%20lathi%20charge%20but%20nothing%20has%20been%20done.%20It%20looks%20like%20the%20government%20is%20playing%20tricks%20on%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20activist%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatil%20added%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fjarangepatil-resumes-hunger-strike-nixes-govt-s-request-to-postpone-it-101698262554126.html%5C%22%3E16%20Marathas%20had%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20the%20government%20had%20done%20nothing%20to%20help%20their%20families.%20He%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20farmers%20who%20suffered%20losses%20to%20their%20crops%20during%20the%20agitation%20be%20compensated%20by%20conducting%20a%20spot%20assessment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minister%20said%20that%20a%20legal%20process%20is%20required%20to%20withdraw%20police%20cases%20and%20that%20the%20concerned%20district%20collectors%20had%20been%20directed%20to%20help%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20died%20by%20suicide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maratha%20quota%20protests%20had%20begun%20on%20August%2029%20when%20Patil%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20Maratha%20activist%20from%20Jalna%2C%20sat%20on%20an%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reviving%20a%20three-decade%20old%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservations.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20agitation%20turned%20violent%20with%20the%20police%20resorting%20to%20lathi-charge%20on%20the%20protesters%2C%20further%20worsening%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmaratha-quota-stir-man-dies-by-suicide-leaves-note-demanding-reservation-for-community%5C%22%3EMaratha%20Quota%20Stir%3A%20Man%20Dies%20by%20Suicide%2C%20Leaves%20Note%20Demanding%20Reservation%20for%20Community%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20apologised%20for%20the%20lathi-charge%20and%20later%20announced%20that%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20will%20be%20issued%20to%20those%20who%20possess%20revenue%20or%20education%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthose-with-nizam-era-documents-recognising-them-as-kunbis-to-get-caste-certificates-cm-shindee%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edocuments%20from%20the%20Nizam%20era%20that%20recognise%20them%20as%20Kunbis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOBC%20organisations%2C%20who%20are%20against%20the%20Marathas%20eating%20into%20their%20share%20of%20the%20quota%2C%20have%20said%20they%20will%20resume%20their%20agitation%20only%20if%20the%20government%20deviates%20from%20its%20written%20assurance%20that%20their%20quota%20will%20not%20be%20touched%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Hindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CUnless%20the%20government%20swerves%20from%20its%20stand%2C%20we%20will%20not%20react%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fjarangepatil-resumes-hunger-strike-nixes-govt-s-request-to-postpone-it-101698262554126.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Babanrao%20Taywade%2C%20president%2C%20OBC%20Mahasangh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20chief%20minister%20Shinde%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minster%20Devendra%20Fadna