-gobsmacked-as-it-charges-extra-fee-for-bad-parenting%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Toccoa%20Riverside%20Restaurant%20in%20the%20Blue%20Ridge%20Mountains%20in%20northern%20Georgia%20will%20levy%20an%20extra%20fee%20for%20customers%20who%20are%20''unable%20to%20parent''%20their%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20photograph%20of%20their%20menu%20circulating%20on%20Reddit%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20amassing%20massive%20criticism%20for%20the%20fee.%20The%20post%20was%20captioned%2C%20''This%20restaurant%20charges%20you%20extra%20for%20bad%20parenting.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20warning%20on%20the%20menu%20bluntly%20states%2C%20''Adult%20surcharge%3A%20For%20adults%20unable%20to%20parent%20%24%24%24.''%20Though%20the%20menu%20doesn't%20reveal%20the%20exact%20amount%2C%20some%20customers%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20charged%20%2450%20(Rs%204%2C160)%20for%20their%20''children's%20behaviour.''%20The%20restaurant%20also%20warns%20customers%20to%20''be%20respectful''%20to%20staff%2C%20property%2C%20and%20themselves%20because%20the%20place%20follows%20a%20''No%20respect%2C%20no%20service''%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22634%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fmildlyinteresting%2Fcomments%2F17f0sxs%2Fthis_restaurant_charges_you_extra_for_bad%2F%5C%22%3EThis%20restaurant%20charges%20you%20extra%20for%20bad%20parenting%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FLPineapplePizzaLover%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FLPineapplePizzaLover%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fmildlyinteresting%2F%5C%22%3Emildlyinteresting%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20angered%20many%20people%2C%20with%20some%20detailing%20their%20experiences%20with%20the%20surcharge%20online.%20According%20to%20its%20reviews%2C%20the%20restaurant%20has%20been%2