d%20%26quot%3Bbring%20our%20captives%20home%26quot%3B%20but%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20detail%20when%2C%20how%20or%20how%20many%26quot%3B%20forces%20would%20take%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20raid%20into%20Gaza%20was%20not%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20military%20told%20AFP.%20But%20it%20was%20likely%20to%20raise%20tensions%20in%20an%20already%20anxious%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20among%20the%20foreign%20leaders%20stepping%20up%20public%20calls%20for%20Israel%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20innocent%20civilians%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20follow%20the%20%26quot%3Blaws%20of%20war%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20pursues%20Hamas%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20he%20had%20privately%20suggested%20Israel%20should%20get%20hostages%20out%20if%20possible%20before%20any%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20their%20decision%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20demand%20it%26quot%3B%2C%20Biden%20said%2C%20as%20he%20called%20on%20Congress%20to%20allocate%20more%20money%20for%20Israeli%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Cairo%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20warned%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20massive%20intervention%20that%20would%20put%20civilian%20lives%20at%20risk%20would%20be%20an%20error.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'It's%20a%20massacre'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza's%20Hamas-controlled%20health%20ministry%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20death%20toll%20had%20surged%20by%20about%20700%20in%20a%20day%20to%20above%206%2C500%2C%20including%20many%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Biden%20has%20stated%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20confidence%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Hamas%20ministry%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20death%20toll%20may%20be%20unclear%2C%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20suffering%20is%20not%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEntire%20neighbourhoods%20have%20been%20razed%2C%20surgeons%