and%20people%20ordered%20to%20shelter%20in%20place%2C%20as%20the%20scourge%20of%20horrifying%20gun%20violence%20once%20again%20ripped%20through%20an%20American%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaine%20public%20safety%20official%20Mike%20Sauschuck%20said%20he%20was%20not%20prepared%20to%20give%20a%20death%20toll%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20fluid%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20reporters%20police%20were%20flooding%20the%20streets%20as%20they%20sought%20the%20gunman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20literally%20hundreds%20of%20police%20officers%20working%20around%20the%20state%20of%20Maine%20to%20investigate%20this%20case%2C%20to%20locate%20Mr.%20Card%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERescue%20vehicles%20rushed%20in%20from%20around%20central%20Maine%20to%20tend%20to%20the%20wounded%2C%20city%20councilor%20McCarthy%20said%2C%20and%20the%20two%20Lewiston%20hospitals%20%26quot%3Bhave%20called%20in%20every%20off-duty%20staff%20member%20that%20they%20could%20to%20deal%20with%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20made%20calls%20--%20stepping%20away%20from%20a%20state%20dinner%20honoring%20Australia's%20prime%20minister%20--%20to%20Maine's%20governor%2C%20its%20two%20senators%20and%20a%20local%20congressman%20to%20offer%20federal%20support%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%20Thursday%2C%20armed%20police%20were%20seen%20guarding%20the%20Central%20Maine%20Medical%20Center%2C%20where%20some%20of%20the%20wounded%20were%20being%20treated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Maine%20school%20boards%20and%20educational%20institutions%2C%20including%20Bates%20College%2C%20said%20they%20would%20not%20be%20holding%20classes%20on%20Thursday%2C%20according%20to%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMultiple%20locations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20and%20rescuers%20reportedly%20arrived%20at%20the%20Sparetime%20Recreation%20bowling%20alley%20at%20about%207%3A