gave%20him%20her%20Parliament%20login%20and%20password%20so%20that%20he%20could%20post%20the%20questions%20directly.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BMahua%20Moitra%20wanted%20to%20quickly%20make%20a%20name%20for%20herself%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20She%20was%20advised%20by%20her%20friends%20and%20advisors%20that%20the%20shortest%20possible%20route%20to%20fame%20is%20by%20personally%20attacking%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20alleged%20in%20the%20affidavit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BMs%20Moitra%20thought%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20attack%20PM%20Modi%20is%20by%20attacking%20Gautam%20Adani%20as%20both%20were%20contemporaries%20and%20belong%20to%20the%20same%20state%20of%20Gujarat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EMr%20Dubey%20and%20Ms%20Moitra%20have%20been%20slugging%20it%20out%20on%20social%20media%20since%20the%20allegations%20surfaced.%20The%20BJP%20MP%20also%20submitted%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20Lokpal%2C%20the%20anti-corruption%20watchdog%20and%20sought%20an%20investigation%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20that%20the%20Lokpal%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20his%20complaint%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Information%20Technology%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20wrote%20to%20Mr%20Dubey%20over%20the%20alleged%20sharing%20of%20her%20parliamentary%20login%20by%20Ms%20Moitra%20and%20said%20the%20matter%20was%20%26quot%3Bof%20grave%20importance%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20the%20National%20Informatics%20Centre%20would%20cooperate%20with%20the%20Parliamentary%20Ethics%20Committee%20in%20investigating%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EMs%20Moitra%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20she%20is%20prepared%20for%20any%20inquiry.%20She%20has%20also%20said%20that%20she%20is%20ready%20to%20answer%20questions%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ENeither%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20nor%20its%20INDIA%20allies%20have%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Ms%20Moitra%20so%20far.%20The%20Trinamool%20has%20said%20it%20will%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20case.%20The%20party's%20leader%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20has%20said%20the%20party%20will%20take%20an%20appropriate%20decision%20on%20the%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%20after%20the%20Parliamentary%20panel%20completes%20its%20investigation.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698304860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fi8bm13i_mahua-moitra-lok-sabha-ani_625x300_04_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-panel-to-hold-first-meet-on-mahua-moitra-bribery-charge-today-4514122%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20is%20recording%20his%20statement%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20in%20the%20first%20meeting%20on%20the%20cash-for-query%20charge%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra.%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20will%20also%20record%20his%20statement%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-panel-to-hold-first-meet-on-mahua-moitra-bribery-charge-today-4514122%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Five%20Nights%20at%20Freddy%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Creepy%20Mascots%20Go%20Rogue%20in%20a