hat%20would%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20horror%3F%20What%20would%20ensure%20that%20human%20life%20is%20not%20wasted%20like%20this%3F%20The%20Israeli%20government%2C%20and%20the%20self-described%20civilised%20nations%20states%20of%20the%20West%2C%20have%20a%20solution.%20It%20involves%20dropping%20bombs%20from%20the%20sky%20on%20a%20thin%20strip%20of%20land%20with%202.3%20million%20people%20walled-in%20from%20all%20sides%2C%20barring%20them%20from%20access%20to%20water%20and%20electricity.%20Hamas%20is%20evil%2C%20and%20this%20is%20how%20you%20destroy%20evil%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Across%20India%2C%20People%20Face%20Charges%20for%20Participating%20in%20Protests%20in%20Support%20of%20Palestine%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-palestine-protests-police-crackdown%5C%22%3EAcross%20India%2C%20People%20Face%20Charges%20for%20Participating%20in%20Protests%20in%20Support%20of%20Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20long%20text%20message%20from%20our%20friend%20Khalil%20from%20Gaza%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOur%20house%2C%20where%20I%20and%20my%20family%20live%2C%20has%20been%20totally%20destroyed%20by%20Israeli%20F16s%2C%20made%20in%20America.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20the%20place%20of%20my%20memories%20with%20my%20late%20father.%20I%20am%20extremely%20sad%20and%20feel%20pain%20deep%20inside%20my%20heart.%20Tears%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20dropping%20off%20my%20eyes.%20I%20can%20feel%20my%20heart%20burning.%20I%20can%20feel%20my%20soul%20being%20suffocated%20by%20this.%20I%20want%20to%20scream%20to%20wake%20the%20world%20up.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENow%2C%20if%20we%20survive%2C%20we%20will%20be%20homeless.%20But%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20the%20hearts%20of%20my%20beloved%20friends%20will%20always%20be%20a%20shelter%20that%20can%20never%20be%20destroyed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20important%20for%20me%20to%20say%20that%20this%20will%20never%20affect%20my%20enthusiasm%20for%20a%20better%20world%20for%20all%20people%20without%20discrimination.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20this%20to%20happen%20to%20any%20person.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EYour%20friend%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKhalil%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20defence%20minister%20also%20has%20a%20message%20for%20everyone%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20imposing%20a%20complete%20siege%20on%20Gaza.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20electricity%2C%20no%20food%2C%20no%20water%2C%20no%20fuel.%20Everything%20will%20be%20closed.%20We%20are%20fighting%20human%20animals%20and%20we%20are%20acting%20accordingly.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20rocket%20from%20Gaza%20is%20intercepted%20by%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system%2C%20I%20can%20hear%20a%20loud%20explosion%20coming%20from%20the%20sky.%20The%20buildings%20shudder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20hear%20a%20sound%20and%20look%20at%20my%20friend.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20thunder%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Only%20now%20do%20I%20notice%20that%20the%20sky%20is%20so%20cloudy%3B%20I%20have%20been%20too%20preoccupied%20with%20reading%20the%20news%20and%20my%20thoughts.%20The%20sounds%20of%20aircrafts%20and%20ambulances%2C%20and%20police%20sirens%20have%20also%20become%20startling.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20that%3F%E2%80%9D%20we%20ask%20each%20other%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20narrow%20and%20long%20bomb%20shelter%20in%20the%20basement%20is%20full%20of%20residents%20from%20the%20floors%20above.%20There%20is%20a%20dog%20here%20too%2C%20who%20seems%20stressed%20out%20by%20the%20crowd%2C%20or%20maybe%20the%20war.%20It%20is%20recommended%20to%20be%20in%20the%20shelter%20for%2010%20minutes%20after%20the%20siren%20sounds.%20Someone%20has%20brought%20a%20plate%20of%20cookies%20to%20share.%20I%20took%20a%20cookie%20and%20now%20this%20dog%20is%20very%20interested%20in%20me.%20A%20friend%20texted%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20am%20okay%20%E2%80%93%20she%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20a%20siren%20in%20my%20area%20because%20of%20an%20app%2C%20which%20notifies%20users%20of%20sirens%20in%20any%20of%20their%20selected%20areas%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20shelter%20seems%20to%20be%20having%20a%20panic%20attack.%20I%20hear%20that%20PTSD%20is%20common%20within%20Israeli%20society.%20Many%20have%20traumatising%20experiences%20during%20their%20mandatory%20military%20service.%20Military%20service%20appears%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20core%20parts%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9CIsraeli%E2%80%9D%3B%20friends%20tell%20me%20that%20when%20strangers%20meet%20they%20often%20try%20to%20find%20mutual%20connections%20by%20referring%20to%20the%20time%20they%20served%20in%20the%20military.%20They%20say%20that%20a%20job%20applicant%20who%20did%20not%20serve%20could%20be%20perceived%20negatively%20by%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20406px)%2085vw%2C%20406px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084900%2FPTLP4329.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22406%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084900%2FPTLP4329.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084900%2FPTLP4329-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084900%2FPTLP4329-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22542%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20map%20of%20Hebron%20created%20by%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%20showing%20the%20architecture%20of%20Israeli%20apartheid.%20Photo%3A%20Aman%20Abhishek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20death%20toll%20is%20still%20rising.%20Nobody%20that%20I%20know%20personally%20has%20been%20physically%20hurt%2C%20but%20almost%20all%20my%20Israeli%20friends%20know%20someone%20who%20died%20or%20is%20missing.%20It%20is%20a%20small%20country%3B%20everyone%20seems%20to%20know%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%E2%80%99s%20mother%20is%20describing%20how%20yesterday%20she%20went%20to%20a%20funeral%20of%20someone%20who%20died%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%20The%20siren%20sounded%20when%20she%20was%20driving%20back%20home%2C%20and%20she%20stopped%20her%20car%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road%20and%20frantically%20searched%20for%20a%20shelter.%20She%20found%20a%20building%20to%20stay%20in%2C%20but%20not%20a%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20large-screen%20TV%20in%20the%20living%20room%20is%20showing%20visuals%20from%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20and%20statements%20from%20Israeli%20officials.%20The%20necessity%20to%20%E2%80%9Cflatten%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdestroy%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cerase%E2%80%9D%20Gaza%20is%20the%20mainstream%20discourse.%20%E2%80%9CCan%20we%20turn%20this%20off%3F%E2%80%9D%20my%20friend%20asks.%20%E2%80%9CI%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20but%20watch%20the%20news.%20It%20is%20hard%20to%20focus%20on%20anything%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20mother%20says.%20She%20has%20turned%20off%20the%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20see%20on%20my%20phone%20that%20a%20former%20board%20member%20of%20the%20leading%20human%20rights%20NGO%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%2C%20Vivian%20Silver%2C%20is%20missing%20since%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207.%20Another%20Israeli%20peace%20activist%2C%20Hayim%20Katsman%2C%20was%20killed%20the%20same%20day.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20him%20but%20my%20friends%20did%2C%20and%20everyone%20is%20in%20shock.%20In%20interviews%20with%20journalists%2C%20Hayim%E2%80%99s%20sibling%20Noy%20said%20to%20not%20%E2%80%9Cuse%20our%20death%20and%20our%20pain%20to%20bring%20the%20death%20and%20pain%20to%20other%20people%20and%20other%20families%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20views%20are%20marginal.%20Joe%20Biden%20just%20gave%20a%20speech%20and%20according%20to%20political%20commentators%2C%20Israelis%20love%20it.%20He%20said%20that%20if%20the%20United%20States%20was%20experiencing%20what%20Israel%20is%20experiencing%2C%20%E2%80%9Cour%20response%20will%20be%20swift%2C%20decisive%2C%20and%20overwhelming.%E2%80%9D%20Like%20after%20September%2011%2C%202001%3F%20When%20two%20decades%20of%20death%20and%20misery%20brought%20by%20the%20US%20response%20%E2%80%93%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9CWar%20on%20Terror%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20concluded%20with%20the%20Taliban%20regaining%20power%20in%20Afghanistan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20What%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20To%20Be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel%3A%20Prof%20Dalal%20Iriqat%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-what-its-like-to-be-a-palestinian-in-israel-prof-dalal-iriqat%5C%22%3EWhat%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20To%20Be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel%3A%20Prof%20Dalal%20Iriqat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20receive%20a%20flood%20of%20messages%20in%20a%20group%20chat.%20A%20Palestinian%20human%20rights%20activist%2C%20Issa%20Amro%2C%20is%20missing.%20Issa%20is%20a%20prominent%20activist%20based%20in%20Hebron%2C%20West%20Bank.%20For%20many%20years%20he%20has%20fought%20against%20Israeli%20apartheid%20as%20well%20as%20human%20rights%20violations%20by%20Palestinian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20group%20consists%20mainly%20of%20Jewish%20peace%20activists%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20I%20know%20and%20have%20become%20friends%20with.%20The%20messages%20are%20describing%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20took%20Issa%20to%20an%20unknown%20location%20and%20nobody%20has%20been%20able%20to%20reach%20him%20for%20hours.%20People%20are%20sending%20worried%20texts%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20should%20we%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhone%20numbers%20of%20military%20offices%20are%20shared%20so%20that%20activists%20could%20call%20and%20ask%20for%20Issa%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts.%20Someone%20calls%20a%20number%20and%20reports%20on%20the%20group%3A%20the%20military%20official%20said%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20time%20to%20entertain%20these%20requests%20during%20wartime.%20Of%20course%20dissent%20and%20human%20rights%20will%20be%20trampled%20using%20the%20pretext%20of%20war%20and%20a%20state%20of%20emergency.%20What%20else%20could%20one%20expect%3F%20This%20is%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20United%20States%20after%20the%20September%2011%20attacks%2C%20and%20it%20happens%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20messages%3A%20the%20Palestinian%20villages%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20where%20Jewish%20activists%20do%20solidarity%20work%20are%20all%20under%20siege.%20Entrances%20to%20many%20Palestinian%20villages%20have%20been%20blocked%2C%20and%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20it%20was%20done%20by%20the%20military%20or%20settlers.%20These%20communities%20are%20unable%20to%20leave%20the%20village%20for%20work%20or%20to%20buy%20daily%20necessities.%20Settlers%20with%20guns%20are%20attacking%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20horrible%20and%20scary%2C%20I%20really%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20write.%20I%20was%20about%20to%20lose%20my%20dad%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20texts%20Sameeha%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20one%20of%20these%20Palestinian%20villages%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20The%20settlers%20tried%20shooting%20her%20father%20today%2C%20and%20they%20shot%20one%20of%20her%20relatives%20at%20point-blank%20range.%20There%20are%20videos%20of%20the%20attacks%2C%20and%20I%20watch%20them%20in%20horror.%20The%20Israeli%20army%20stood%20by%20and%20did%20nothing%3B%20a%20soldier%20even%20shook%20hands%20with%20the%20settlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20really%20bad%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20texts%20another%20Palestinian.%20As%20the%20attention%20shifts%20to%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20is%20getting%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Israeli%20Settlers%20Are%20Using%20the%20Ongoing%20Violence%20to%20Ethnically%20Cleanse%20Palestinians%20in%20Jordan%20Valley%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraeli-settlers-are-using-the-ongoing-violence-to-ethnically-cleanse-palestinians-in-jordan-valley%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20Settlers%20Are%20Using%20the%20Ongoing%20Violence%20to%20Ethnically%20Cleanse%20Palestinians%20in%20Jordan%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20is%20rising%20rapidly%2C%20and%20at%20this%20rate%2C%20it%20will%20cross%20the%20Israeli%20casualties%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20Sometimes%20we%20can%20hear%20explosions%20but%20there%20are%20no%20sirens.%20Where%20was%20the%20explosion%2C%20then%3F%20My%20friend%E2%80%99s%20mother%20thinks%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20sound%20of%20the%20bombs%20that%20are%20being%20dropped%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20reaching%20us%20all%20the%20way%20here%2C%20in%20Central%20Israel.%20I%20do%20not%20know%20if%20that%20is%20possible%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20heart-wrenching%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Faman-abhishek%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAman%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Abhishek%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20PhD%20student%20in%20media%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Madison%2C%20USA.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698294647000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084733%2FIMG_6962.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwar-will-surely-bring-peace-this-time-notes-from-israel-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Palestinian%20villages%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20where%20Jewish%20activists%20do%20solidarity%20work%20are%20all%20under%20siege.%20Entrances%20to%20many%20Palestinian%2