12.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332695%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20team%20arrived%20in%20the%20district%2C%20villagers%20and%20locals%20were%20highly%20sceptical%20on%20whether%20such%20work%20could%20be%20done%20with%20community%20participation%20and%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20an%20NGO.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20PPP%20work%3A%20Samast%20Mahajan%2C%20A.T.E.%20Chandra%20Foundation%20and%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20those%20lamenting%20the%20failure%20of%20public%20and%20private%20partnerships%20in%20India%2C%20the%20water%20rejuvenation%20efforts%20of%20Maharashtra%20offers%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope.%20It%20was%20in%202013%20that%20Bain%20Capital%20chairman%20Amit%20Chandra%20%E2%80%94%20who%20set%20up%20and%20finances%20the%20A.T.E.%20Chandra%20foundation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Archana%2C%20started%20questioning%20why%20despite%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%20and%20bluster%2C%20farmer%20suicides%20in%20the%20drought-hit%20state%20refused%20to%20abate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20rocket%20science%20to%20reach%20a%20quick%20answer-%20poor%20rainfall%20%3D%20failed%20crop%20season%20%3D%20farmer%20debt%20%3D%20farmer%20suicide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20they%20came%20across%20another%20NGO%20already%20working%20on%20the%20simple%20model%20they%20have%20since%20adopted-%20silt%20removal%20and%20rejuvenation%20of%20water%20bodies.%20Primary%20research%20done%20by%20them%20showed%20that%20there%20are%20many%20water%20bodies%20across%20the%20country%20that%20have%20over%20the%20years%20become%20defunct%20or%20unable%20to%20hold%20much%20water%20due%20to%20heavy%20silting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20groundwater%20too%20fails%20to%20get%20recharged%20as%20the%20silt%20prevents%20the%20rainwater%20from%20reaching%20the%20bottom.%20But%20if%20someone%20removed%20the%20silt%2C%20the%20water%20body%20could%20be%20rejuvenated%20and%20even%20better%20the%20silt%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20usually%20quite%20fertile%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20used%20by%20farmers%20on%20their%20land%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F268059%2Fmeena-pawar-nashik-farmer-earns-lakhs-grape-debt-farming-success-story-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprove%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%202016%20to%202019%2C%20the%20A.T.E%20CF%2C%20along%20with%2022-odd%20partner%20organisations%2C%20worked%20extensively%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20rejuvenate%20over%202%2C700%20water%20bodies%2C%20impacting%20around%204%2C200%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20dampened%20their%20efforts%20but%20did%20not%20stop.%20In%202020%20and%202021%2C%20work%20continued%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Karnataka.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20work%20picked%20up%20pace%20once%20again%20and%20916%20water%20bodies%20were%20rejuvenated%20in%2018%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20some%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Niti%20Aayog%20which%20had%2C%20by%20then%2C%20pulled%20in%20by%20the%20foundation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-17-at-10.00.31_11zon-1697801718.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20India%20is%20placed%20at%20120th%20amongst%20122%20countries%20in%20the%20water%20quality%20index%2C%20with%20nearly%2070%25%20of%20water%20being%20contaminated.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-17-at-10.00.31_11zon-1697801718.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%